List of Features (Not an exhaustive list)

Account Features
Create, delete accounts (speaker / attendee / organizer)
Reset password
VIP accounts that can attend VIP exclusive events.

Message
Send message between users
Send message to attendees in one event
Send message to all speakers (by organizers)
Add / remove contact list
Archive messages, remove from archive (phase 2)
Direct reply to a message (phase 2)
Unread/ read messages (phase 2)
Delete messages (phase 2)

Event
Extra requirements
Dietary restrictions
Accessibility requirements
Approve any pending requirements
Specifications for room type, and showing rooms for an event based on room type

General
Divided controller up by each submenu (AccountMenu, MessageMenu, EventMenu)
Added presenter class
These consist of text required by methods of all submenus and Eventsystem